Subject: [PATCH 0831/1594] ENGR00306443-1 mx6sx:Update the gc400t QoS

commit 200377cc079f39cfab328a86e7eed5ff8e607a9c from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git

(cherry-pick from f3f7f04e644d20c6483232eeb8da91ad8905d23b)

